    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375810/extras/25aa75b5bf165b71cce0a564e9454c7e.poster.avif?t=1730458110\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375810/extras/25aa75b5bf165b71cce0a564e9454c7e.webm?t=1730458110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375810/extras/25aa75b5bf165b71cce0a564e9454c7e.mp4?t=1730458110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the discord invite link to join the discord chat where I'll post about new updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375810/extras/50599f3643772c097e96e41bce9b8fd2.avif?t=1730458110\" width=489 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight massive swarms of bots with varying behaviours. Build overpowered weapons to survive and get to the boss bot. Aim your weapon to make the most of each shot and fill the screen with bullets. Can you survive the unique challenges of each map as the bots change their tactics and grow stronger and greater in numbers?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from tons of upgradeable weapon mods and character upgrades to create a unique build each game. Dodge around movable obstacles, use them as cover, or destroy them. Find rare weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore each new map, you can recruit new characters with unique abilities and traits to help you survive longer and beat each boss. Enemies and items drop scrap metal which you can use to unlock new weapons and upgrades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375810/extras/08f460a2eeca1719049a596a689202da.avif?t=1730458110\" width=489 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number of bots is growing out of control. Huge factories produce them endlessly. We have to destroy them so that they don't take over the world.</p>",
